{"tid":521857,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【關你鬼事咩回教徒】巴勒斯坦人伯利恆示威抗議東正教賣地給以色列","createTime":"2018-01-07T03:44:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-08T03:13:19.000Z","uid":20816,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"58ba26face01bcbea915e90ea69eee161dd90f1b","tid":521857,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:44:00.000Z","msg":"東正教將今日定為教會聖誕日，中東多處都有慶祝活動，不過在伯利恆，大批巴勒斯坦人杯葛慶祝活動，抗議東正教會向以色列出售土地。有信徒在耶路撒冷，趁東正教宗主教奧斐洛三世，乘座駕到伯利恆主誕堂途中，圍堵主教座駕表達不滿，期間與保安人員推撞，又向車隊投擲雜物，巴勒斯坦警方到場阻止示威者靠近車隊。<br />\n<br />\n東正教會是以色列第二大地主，擁有耶路撒冷舊城區三成土地。傳媒早前揭發教會負債數千萬美元，要秘密出售資產還債。有份示威的信眾批評教會賤賣資產，將土地賣給以色列及猶太人，是背叛巴勒斯坦的行為，要求主教下台及取消有關交易。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=985817&amp;csid=261_367\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D985817%26csid%3D261_367&d=eb5wZcAy4fJdVWHKthXoKoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=e7b4585e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=985817&amp;csid=261_367</a>"},{"pid":"c08a50618d9cc25e8ea8ce3238048490fd289b2f","tid":521857,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:00:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d702aa5fa4ecb958169fa71c87426c995f29c0c1","tid":521857,"uid":12853,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T09:05:28.000Z","msg":"最鬼惡既宗教"},{"pid":"7e059668bd629fd84af7dac4838488fba48f995b","tid":521857,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-08T03:13:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}